---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Origin Direct Group"
  description="Privacy policy for Origin Direct Group. How we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
>
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-gray">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-brand-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">When you submit a quote request through our website, we collect the following information:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-1">
        <li>Company name</li>
        <li>Email address</li>
        <li>Phone number (if provided)</li>
        <li>Product and quantity requirements</li>
        <li>Destination country</li>
        <li>Any additional information you provide in the message field</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We use your information solely to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-1">
        <li>Respond to your quote requests</li>
        <li>Provide pricing and product information</li>
        <li>Facilitate commodity transactions</li>
        <li>Communicate about your orders and shipments</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. Data Storage</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Form submissions are processed through Formspree and stored securely. We retain your information only as long as necessary to fulfill your request and maintain business records.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">This website does not use tracking cookies or third-party analytics. We use only essential cookies required for the website to function.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">You have the right to request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data. To exercise these rights, please contact us through our quote form.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">For privacy-related inquiries, please submit a request through our <a href="/quote" class="text-brand-700 hover:text-brand-600 underline">contact form</a>.</p>

      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-8">Origin Direct Group<br />Unit 2201, 22/F Chung Kiu Comm. Bldg.<br />47-51 Shan Tung St. Mongkok<br />Hong Kong</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
